    "description": "BEL Ventures Solutions has an exciting opening for a Backend Developer at our Meerut office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout BEL Ventures Solutions:\nBEL Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in Java\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Meerut, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with BEL Ventures Solutions!",
